        "description": "<p><em>Thunder Desert GP</em> is an arcade motorcycle racing game very similar to <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/3343/super-hang-on/\">Super Hang-On</a>. It is largely a remake of one of the previous games by the developer, <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/?q=Grand+Prix\">Grand Prix</a>, but with motorcycles instead of cars and different scenery.</p>\n<p>The game is set in a desert environment. The goal is to complete ten laps and win the gold cup before time runs out. After each lap the timer is reset. There is an endless amount of opponents on the track that need to be avoided. Others dangers are signs that can cause crashes and getting off the road slows down the biker as well. There are sometimes small dunes that provide a jump and some sections take the bike through a tunnel. The game is controlled with the two analog sticks: the left for steering and the right for accelerating and braking.</p>",
